<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>Upgraded Ccomputers</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.6.3/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-UHRtZLI+pbxtHCWp1t77Bi1L4ZtiqrqD80Kn4Z8NTSRyMA2Fd33n5dQ8lWUE00s/" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/3.5.2/animate.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="public/css/style.css">
  <link rel="icon" href="public/images/favicon.ico">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="brand"><span>Upgraded</span> Computers</h1>
    <h3><span class="txt-type" data-wait="3000" data-words='["Welcome", "Lets get started", "I am sure we can help You!"]'></span></h3>
    <div class="aboutus">
        <div class="centertext">You have had your computer for a while now and it just seems to be running slower and slower each day. You are nearing the point, where you
            just want to give up. It's frustrating, but what can you do. You know the computer shops ask a lot of money to upgrade, and normally they just want to sell you
            a new computer anyway. If only they understood, that you are on a budget and can't afford to buy that fancy smancy computer. 
        </div>
        <div><img src="public/images/computer.jpg" alt="Inside of a computer"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="aboutus">
        <div><img src="public/images/achievement.jpg" alt="Inside of a computer"></div>
        <div class="centertext">This is where we come in. We will search the internet for the best available deals and send you a quote, based on your budget. Once you are happy
            and payment has been made, we will get you up and running in no time. 
        </div>
        
    </div>
    <p class="email-sent">{{ msg }}</p>

    <div id="my-modal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="wrapper animated bounceInLeft">
                
                <div class="company-info">
                    <h3>To get started:</h3>
                    <ul>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-angle-right"></i> Enter your details</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-angle-right"></i> Click <strong>SUBMIT</strong></li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-angle-right"></i> Wait for our reply</li>
                    </ul>
                    <small>Your information is for our eyes only!</small>
                </div>
                <div class="contact">
                  <span class="close">&times;</span>
                    <h3>Email Us</h3>
                    <form method="POST" action="send">
                    <p>
                        <label>Full Name</label>
                        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="John Doe" required maxlength="40">
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <label>Email Address</label>
                        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="jdoe@mail.com" required maxlength="50">
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <label>Phone Number</label>
                        <input type="number" name="phone" placeholder="082 123 4567" required oninput="javascript: if (this.value.length > this.maxLength) this.value = this.value.slice(0, this.maxLength);"
                        type = "number"
                        maxlength = "10">
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <label>Budget available</label>
                        <input type="number" name="company" placeholder="2500.00" required oninput="javascript: if (this.value.length > this.maxLength) this.value = this.value.slice(0, this.maxLength);"
                        type = "number"
                        maxlength = "8">
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <label>Computer used for</label>
                        <select name="usage" id="usage">
                            <option value="Gaming">Gaming</option>
                            <option value="HomeOffice">Home/Office</option>
                        </select>
                    </p>
                    <p>
                    <label>Location</label>
                        <select name="location" id="location">
                            <option value="Gauteng">Gauteng</option>
                            <option value="Western Cape">Western Cape</option>
                            <option value="Northern Cape">Northern Cape</option>
                            <option value="North West">North West</option>
                            <option value="Free State">Free State</option>
                            <option value="Eastern Cape">Eastern Cape</option>
                            <option value="Kwazulu Natal">Kwazulu Natal</option>
                            <option value="Mpumalanga">Mpumalanga</option>
                            <option value="Limpopo">Limpopo</option>
                        </select>
                    </p>
                    <p class="full">
                        <label>Message</label>
                        <textarea name="message" rows="5" placeholder="My computer is running slow and I want to upgrade... OR I am looking for a second hand / new computer..." required maxlength="400"></textarea>
                    </p>
                    <p class="full">
                        <button type="submit">Submit</button>
                    </p>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p>You can contact us by sending an email to <a class="contact-email" href="mailto:admin@easyup.co.za">admin@easyup.co.za</a> or by clicking the button below.</p>
    <button id="modal-btn" class="button">Contact Us Form</button>

  </div>
  <footer>
      <div class="container">
          <div><strong>Disclaimer:</strong>  We will do our best to make sure you get the result you are looking for. Sometimes we purchase new parts and other times we 
              will look at the second hand market, but you will always be informed of what we are doing and what the costs are.
          </div>
      </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="public/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>